<blockquote> <p>Competencies: Verbal communication, Self development- awareness of strengths and areas for development, pursuing and applying feedback, multi-tasking in a fast-paced environment, maintaining a successful personal brand while providing critical feedback,
        Professionalism - Being present and prepared, prioritizing and completing tasks to accomplish goals.</p> 
        <p>Students choose a geometric shape and and color theory to create a visually interesting acrylic painting. They apply color choice as a response to the compositional placement - color by color. Students must decide when an area will be repainted with a new color as the painting develops. No color studies are made before beginning the final painting, so students are reacting to color and composition on the painting surface.</p></blockquote>

</worksheet>
